Author: Mylo#8306
Content:
Yes the lists compiled have not looked at the data.
The list from https://komodoelection.com/candidates/

Author: Mylo#8306
Content: uses this git command to list activity on the proposal at the first instance of becoming a candidate.

Author: Mylo#8306
Content:
```
for i in  `git log --pretty=format: --name-only --since="43 days ago" | grep notarynodes | grep -i "README.md"  | sort | uniq`
```

Author: Mylo#8306
Content: for this year, this is all we can manage - the election process began with no meta-data to help with the advertisements.  this is something for next year, unless every NN proposal wants to update with some meta data info
